thread.title: BRIEF-Wuhan Yangtze Communication Industry Group sees FY 2017 net profit to up 290 pct to 333 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Wuhan Yangtze Communication Industry Group sees FY 2017 net profit to up 290 pct to 333 pct

organizations.name: reuters) - wuhan yangtze communication industry group co ltd

text:
Feb 1 (Reuters) - Wuhan Yangtze Communication Industry Group Co Ltd :
* Sees FY 2017 net profit to increase by 290 percent to 333 percent
* Says FY 2016 net profit was 63.5 million yuan
* Says performance of main business and gain from sale of equities in units as main reasons for the forecast
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/duHu3L
